{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cb8d1f789d","title":"转发山东省委关于抗旱夏种的紧急通知的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2c8420d9a2","index":0,"year":1955,"month":7,"day":2,"articleId":"cb8d1f789d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji35":{"comments":[{"id":"1dbf0df80f","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"cb8d1f789d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央秘书长、国务院副总理。"},{"id":"8fb9b8226a","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"cb8d1f789d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共山东省委1955年6月29日关于当前抗早夏种给所属地、市委并报中央的紧急通知。通知指出，目前全省灾情严重，已播的春苗缺水枯姜，如再有半月持续不雨，将造成大阜。因此要求在一切阜灾地区，全力突击抗旱播种。地、县委负责同志要深入灾区，大力发动群众，坚定干部群众的抗早信心。同时要积极准备播种晚秋作物，力争减少损失。省委决定增拨各地抗旱贷款一百万元，专款专用。责成各地供销社大力收购晚秋作物种子，以保证晚秋作物及时播种。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a96f50ed96","type":"title","text":"转发山东省委关于抗旱夏种的紧急通知的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"cb8d1f789d"},{"id":"1dbf0df80f","type":"paragraph","text":"小平同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"cb8d1f789d"},{"id":"8fb9b8226a","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请转发河南、陕西两省委作参考。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"cb8d1f789d"},{"id":"6133cad31b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"cb8d1f789d"},{"id":"991878244a","type":"paragraph","text":"七月二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"cb8d1f789d"}],"page":{"id":"aaf1b17abc","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"cb8d1f789d","start":184,"end":184}}}},"__N_SSG":true}